- New maintainer: Francesco Ariis <fa-ml@ariis.it>.
- New repo: https://gitlab.com/fffaaa/utf8-light.
- Added minimal testuite.
- Added README and NEWS.
- utf8-light now should wordk with both GHC≥9.2 and GHC<9.2.
